{"tid":1862190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陽江核電站二號機組　計算機信息和控制系統服務器故障","createTime":"2020-02-04T13:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T03:56:32.000Z","uid":210140,"like":121,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcf8556e093f5925619909bdce72ff7665f6e72","tid":1862190,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"保安局發言人今日（2月4日）表示，陽江核電有限公司今日在其網站內，通報了一則有關陽江核電站的運行事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據與電網商定的計劃，陽江核電站二號機組新春期間處於停機備用狀態。2月2日，二號機組計算機信息和控制系統服務器出現故障，工作人員及時切換至後備控制系統，繼續監控機組狀態。該故障很快得到排除處理，系統及時恢復可用。故障處理期間，二號機組始終處於安全狀態。  <br />\n<br />\n 以上事件發生後，陽江核電公司已將有關資訊及時向相關的政府監管部門報告。根據國際核和放射事件分級表以及核安全法規，事件界定為「0級」，對機組安全運行、員工健康、周邊公眾和環境沒有造成影響<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-04-2020/59705?fbclid=IwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F02-04-2020%2F59705%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=e89ca44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-04-2020/59705?fbclid=IwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母我唔想肺炎完又中輻射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b3a3b47bb1edb79ff0dfc16ee914e9bf8dd1b8","tid":1862190,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead14688a0eb60fce2a0ca4c60bf60908f50e207","tid":1862190,"uid":197640,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"7dcf8556e093f5925619909bdce72ff7665f6e72","tid":1862190,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"保安局發言人今日（2月4日）表示，陽江核電有限公司今日在其網站內，通報了一則有關陽江核電站的運行事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據與電網商定的計劃，陽江核電站二號機組新春期間處於停機備用狀態。2月2日，二號機組計算機信息和控制系統服務器出現故障，工作人員及時切換至後備控制系統，繼續監控機組狀態。該故障很快得到排除處理，系統及時恢復可用。故障處理期間，二號機組始終處於安全狀態。  <br />\n<br />\n 以上事件發生後，陽江核電公司已將有關資訊及時向相關的政府監管部門報告。根據國際核和放射事件分級表以及核安全法規，事件界定為「0級」，對機組安全運行、員工健康、周邊公眾和環境沒有造成影響<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-04-2020/59705?fbclid=IwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F02-04-2020%2F59705%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=e89ca44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-04-2020/59705?fbclid=IwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母我唔想肺炎完又中輻射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"輻射會殺晒病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df045ce72df9e8f74520efc3b91e56abf8cea01","tid":1862190,"uid":137569,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mmF2UmN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmmF2UmN.jpg&h=4618ea67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"586bae452dd2fe5ca980c970eadd90ca805620de","tid":1862190,"uid":41988,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNEZWAj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNEZWAj.gif&h=6a60713f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60a9a556980fc9da17f3f579438665d0f8db1d4d","tid":1862190,"uid":55458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T1