hopping買無謂野， 男人為咗屌閪又不斷課金，結果最後都係攬炒<br />\n<br />\n重要係咁生仔女"},{"pid":"479221e336739bd0ceface7d9955cf85a71eafe2","tid":1862190,"uid":48132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"fall out"},{"pid":"3fc70daa335ae831e5395d9fe69b8cd1b54e7378","tid":1862190,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n聯署要求世衛主席辭職<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=a7dc6140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general</a><br />\n<br />\n美孚手足被爆頭要推上 twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Domo96954201/status/1223987271344390144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDomo96954201%2Fstatus%2F1223987271344390144&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=dae4ef74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDomo96954201%2Fstatus%2F1223987271344390144&h=df720d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Domo96954201/status/1223987271344390144</a><br />\n<br />\n加入工會，組織力量<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=b455da22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"b7447f3e983a4eb204f869e9a038e7ba860256da","tid":1862190,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"水霸會唔會缺⋯"},{"pid":"c3e0cf6d6e58128949cbccff39164347c9ff5143","tid":1862190,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9774280d9cfd325afa4c0d7b63c4e63fc401bf05","tid":1862190,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dcf8556e093f5925619909bdce72ff7665f6e72","tid":1862190,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"保安局發言人今日（2月4日）表示，陽江核電有限公司今日在其網站內，通報了一則有關陽江核電站的運行事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據與電網商定的計劃，陽江核電站二號機組新春期間處於停機備用狀態。2月2日，二號機組計算機信息和控制系統服務器出現故障，工作人員及時切換至後備控制系統，繼續監控機組狀態。該故障很快得到排除處理，系統及時恢復可用。故障處理期間，二號機組始終處於安全狀態。  <br />\n<br />\n 以上事件發生後，陽江核電公司已將有關資訊及時向相關的政府監管部門報告。根據國際核和放射事件分級表以及核安全法規，事件界定為「0級」，對機組安全運行、員工健康、周邊公眾和環境沒有造成影響<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-04-2020/59705?fbclid=IwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F02-04-2020%2F59705%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=e89ca44d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-04-2020/59705?fbclid=IwAR0uDDwiBjADQWx04mVXVa4IhHCj1qTBmbKAkHmOS0ZQhfmCmUwzs25cyHQ</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母我唔想肺炎完又中輻射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:42:01.000Z","msg":"都未出事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"你肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8167186882be6374b8fe99b7c44b2295fcbe6e","tid":1862190,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:2